  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is aim to determine the sodium intake in Ecuadorian population that is an unknown
      information at present. For that, 24h urine samples will be collected from 130 subjects
      working either at tue USFQ or HDLV to measure sodium excretion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
